::Magmatron::

    He went back to his lab, since he could control Bobertron with a thought. 
In the lab was what he was working on before he left. Phobias Spider Spy. He 
looked in to it's Optics. He had changed it to trasmit false information to 
whoever was listening. It would also track it, but only if the person was in 
a certain area. It was also programmed to spread the virus with any of the 
other ones, so hopefully soon all the bugs in his base would be infected.
